title: On website example Tree comparison fails
body:
by **sjh.android.2**: 
What steps will reproduce the problem?
1. Browse to http://golang.org/
2. Select "Tree Comparison" in dropdown
3. Click Compile &  Run

What is the expected output?
Correct compilation and 4 reports on tree comparison

What do you see instead?
prog.go:55: undefined: closed
prog.go:56: undefined: closed

Please provide any additional information below.
Browser is Google Chrome 11.0.696.60 unknown
OS is Windows Vista Enterprise SP2
